      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump — the same geometry family as the subject device. Operating conditions span the clinical CPB range (2–6 L/min, 2000–4000 RPM). Porcine blood used in experiments is an accepted analogue for human blood in hemolysis studies per ISO 10993-4 guidance."
